  [2]: https://stackoverflow.com/q/4332264/426371
  [3]: https://stackoverflow.com/a/6603018/14955
  [4]: https://bugs.openjdk.java.net/browse/JDK-8028683
  [5]: https://bugs.openjdk.java.net/browse/JDK-4724038

